185B4CB2.Line7.10FAE8: Light protect you in these dark days.

3FD7A2F0.Line5.10FAE8: I offer what shelter I can here, but we are never far from Mephisto's influence. His temptations.

6753F92E.Line3.10FAE8: Heed my warning. Hatred is a poison you drink to kill someone else. It will tear you apart, as surely as your enemies.

8ED04F6C.Line1.10FAE8: So, you feel it, too? Hatred... boiling just beneath the surface of this wretched place.

DF067B39.VoiceDir1.10FAE8: Calm and collected. This priest offers a safety and sanctuary in a violent, cursed land
